om/nRzH4t7wCk2ZpzGAkm-ty_Qz-fQ=/750x750/2c700aa5-ffdf-49dd-b981-22e55e5ee407--2021-0503_beehive-alchemy_tapered-beeswax-candles_spring-mixed_1x1_ty-mecham.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Ty Mecham\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \n\n\n  \n\n              \u003ch2\u003e3. Make Bud Vases Your Secret Weapon\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eA few stems in small vases \u0026gt; one giant arrangement. This is truly the easiest way to make a table feel fresh, fun, and springy. I grab a few $3.99 bunches at Trader Joe’s and break them up into several vessels.\nLine them down the table, mix heights, and save one to tuck in the bathroom (it’s all about the \u003cem\u003esurprise flower moment\u003c/em\u003e), and if you’re feeling fancy, tie a sprig into each napkin.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width